OL,7,FPolice have been advised to publicly
OL,8,Fshare the ethnicity and nationality of
OL,9,Fsuspects charged in high profile cases
OL,10,Fin a bid to curb misinformation
OL,11,Fspreading online.
OL,13,FThe guidance, which is effective
OL,14,Fimmediately, has been issued from the
OL,15,FNational Police Chiefs' Council (NPCC)
OL,16,Fand the College of Policing after
OL,17,Fmounting pressure on police over the
OL,18,Fdetails they make public.
