OL,7,FThere has been growing criticism of
OL,8,Fthe police handling of incidents in
OL,9,Frecent weeks, especially the case of
OL,10,Ftwo men reportedly Afghan asylum
OL,11,Fseekers who were charged with the rape
OL,12,Fof a 12-year-old girl in Warwickshire.
OL,14,FReform UK accused Warwickshire police
OL,15,Fof a 'cover up' and withholding
OL,16,Finformation, which the force denied.
