OL,7,F"Disinformation and incorrect
OL,8,Fnarratives can take hold in a vacuum.
OL,10,F"It is good police work for us to fill
OL,11,Fthis vacuum with the facts about
OL,12,Fissues of wider public interest."
OL,14,FEmily Spurrell, of the Association of
OL,15,FPolice and Crime Commissioners,
OL,16,Fwelcomed the new guidance.
