OL,7,F"PCCs and Deputy Mayors act on behalf
OL,8,Fof the public and it is clear there
OL,9,Fwas a need to review the guidance to
OL,10,Faddress growing public concern," she
OL,11,Fsaid.
OL,13,F"We have seen the speed with which mis
OL,14,For disinformation can spread online
OL,15,Fand the danger to public safety that
OL,16,Fcan cause, so it is right police keep
OL,17,Fthe public informed as far as is
OL,18,Fpossible whilst preserving a suspect's
OL,19,Fright to a fair trial."
